"A.D.2028/4/2/17:00": "It doesn't look like a search was conducted here... I hope that my situation hasn't spread throughout the school."
"Wait, what am I saying? That's something that I need to deal with later. For now, I need to see my big bro."
"Oh my, if it isn't Miss Yasaka?"
"Your words are quite inappropriate Miss Yasaka. I heard that you've been away for Student Council duties, but... What are you doing here?"
"Eh- Student Council duties? Who told you that?"
"Miss Washinomiya did. She's not with you at the moment?"
"This is problematic. Your older brother just came here but, I told him that you were away."
"Yes, he came by earlier. He asked for your current whereabouts and I responded with that but..."
"Ah, that's alright. Fortunately, I have some business with my big bro, I'll go meet him instead. By the way, where is he?"
"He told me that he was heading back to the Men's Dormitory. Well then, Miss Yasaka, I'll take my leave now."
